    <description>This is a Schedule-Triggered Flow.
The flow starts with a scheduled trigger, running every week on October 3, 2024, at 1:00 PM. It checks Device Compliance records for seven conditions, including statuses like &apos;noncompliant&apos;, &apos;Not Compatible&apos;, &apos;Not Encrypted&apos;, and &apos;false&apos;. If the record meets these criteria, it&apos;s added to a compliance issue collection. The flow then loops through each record in the collection, updating the Compliance_Issue__c field with the collected issues.

Several objects and their fields worth mentioning. Below are the details (the format is given as: object_name - field_name: interaction)
  * [&apos;Device_Compliance__c&apos;, &apos;WS1_Device_Compliance_Status__c, Windows_11_Readiness_Status__c, WS1_BitLocker_Encryption_Status__c, WS1_Device_Enrollment_Status__c, WS1_Encryption_Status__c, WS1_Aging__c&apos;]
  * [&apos;Device_Compliance__c&apos;, &apos;ReportDate__c&apos;]</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>ComplianceIssues</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
    {!$Record.WS1_Device_Compliance_Status__c} = &apos;Noncompliant&apos;,
    &apos;Noncompliant&apos;,
    &apos;&apos;
) &amp;

IF(
    AND(
        {!$Record.WS1_Device_Compliance_Status__c} = &apos;Noncompliant&apos;,
        OR(
            {!$Record.Windows_11_Readiness_Status__c} = &apos;Not Compatible&apos;,
            {!$Record.WS1_BitLocker_Encryption_Status__c} = &apos;Not Encrypted&apos;,
            {!$Record.WS1_Device_Enrollment_Status__c} != &apos;Enrolled&apos;,
            {!$Record.WS1_Encryption_Status__c} = &apos;Not Encrypted&apos;,
            {!$Record.WS1_Aging__c} &gt;= 90
        )
    ),
    &apos;; &apos;,
    &apos;&apos;
) &amp;

IF(
    {!$Record.WS1_Bitlocker_Encryption_Method__c} = &apos;XTS-AES 128 bit&apos;,
    &apos;Bitlocker Encryption Method&apos;,
    &apos;&apos;
)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>WeekAgoDate</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>TODAY() - 7</expression>
    </formulas>
